LoreSourceControl is an independently authored Unreal Engine editor plugin.

This repository intentionally does not include Epic Games source-file copyright
notices, copied Epic Games provider implementation code, or Unreal Engine source
files. It references Unreal Engine public interfaces by include name only and is
intended to be compiled by users who already have access to their own Unreal
Engine installation.

